            "type": "text",
            "text": " — the ability to derive new conclusions rather than recall stored ones. ARC-AGI tests pure inductive abstraction; MATH/AIME test symbolic mathematical reasoning; HotpotQA and MuSiQue test multi-hop factual chaining; StrategyQA and LogiQA test commonsense and formal deduction. Chain-of-thought prompting and self-consistency improve scores across all categories. For agents that must plan, debug, or solve open-ended problems, strong reasoning benchmark performance is a reliable predictor of real-world task success."
